videos.headline: Penn State picks off Rutgers' overthrow
videos.description: Rutgers QB Artur Sitkowski airmails a pass into coverage and John Reid intercepts it for Penn State.

videos.headline: Sitkowski's 2nd pick leads to Penn State TD
videos.description: QB Artur Sitkowski is picked off for the second time, leading to Trace McSorley's touchdown pass on the ensuing drive.

videos.headline: Rutgers DB steals ball out of receiver's hand
videos.description: QB Trace McSorley tosses up a 50-50 ball that Rutgers DB Isaiah Wharton steals out of the receiver's hands.

videos.headline: TE Freiermuth snags 2nd TD of game
videos.description: Penn State TE Pat Freiermuth reaches up to grab his second touchdown of the afternoon, giving them a 20-0 lead.

videos.headline: Rutgers erases shutout with 2-yard TD
videos.description: RB Raheem Blackshear punches it in from 2 yards out to erase Rutgers' goose egg on the board.
